# Task 11B Path A baseline-only expected-output tracking whitelist (Amendment 5 / §16.9.2).
# Path-precise: tracks ONLY backend/tests/evaluation/data/expected/baseline_feasible.v1.json.
# Does NOT un-ignore the whole data/expected/ directory, any other JSON, or any
# downstream change. high_throughput_review.v1.json MUST NOT be added through this
# whitelist; it requires a separate Amendment and a separate whitelist entry per
# §16.9.4 future-restoration conditions.
!backend/tests/evaluation/data/
backend/tests/evaluation/data/*
!backend/tests/evaluation/data/expected/
backend/tests/evaluation/data/expected/*
!backend/tests/evaluation/data/expected/baseline_feasible.v1.json

